MAJOR LEAGUES PLAYING BALL WITH CASTRO

John Berlau tells us that Cuban defectors are singled out for substandard 
treatment by Major League Baseball. Orioles owner Peter Angelos says his special 
relationship with Castro has nothing to do with it.

http://www.insightmag.com/news/252748.html

